    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Bundamedik Tbk provides health care services in Indonesia. It also engages private hospital and healthcare support service activities; provision of ambulance services; private health education; consultant for reproductive technology services management; management consultant of physiotherapy service; and hotel, and dental clinic services management consulting businesses. It also provides fertility clinic, and oncology; emergency services; laboratory, radiology, and IVF services; and genomics and clinical pathology laboratory, and corporate health services. In addition, the company operates a BMHS nurse center, bunda neuro centre, bunda heart centre, bunda urology centre, digital substraction angiography, RSM oncology, and advanced robotic minimal invasive surgery. PT Bundamedik Tbk was founded in 1961 and is based in Jakarta Pusat, Indonesia. PT Bundamedik Tbk is a subsidiary of PT Bunda Investama Indonesia.",
